data.description: Welcome to this inviting Completely updated 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom (plus den/office & bonus room) haven nestled in the heart of Parrish, Florida. This beautiful home boasts the perfect blend of modern living and cozy comfort.    As you step inside, you're greeted by a spacious, open-concept living area, allowing natural light to grace every corner. The well-appointed completely updated kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring sleek countertops, ample storage, and top-of-the-line appliances, making every meal a delight to prepare.    The inviting bedrooms offer ample space and comfort, providing a retreat for relaxation and rest. The master suite is a true oasis, complete with an ensuite updated bathroom, ensuring a private and serene escape.    Offering a formal dining room, spacious den or office currently utilized as an additional bedroom and a bonus room, this Parrish home has plenty of space for all!    But the true gem of this property lies outside, where a sparkling pool beckons for endless enjoyment and entertaining under the Florida sun. Surrounded by lush landscaping, this outdoor oasis is perfect for gatherings, relaxation, and creating lasting memories with family and friends.    Other important info: Pool resurfaced 1 year ago, roof 3 years new, HVAC 5 years new    Located in a desirable area of Parrish, this home offers not just a place to live, but a lifestyle to embrace. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home sweet home.
